<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 15 at 9:07AM EST  by NWS Raleigh</headline>
<description>...Patchy dense fog across the Piedmont this morning...
Patchy dense fog has developed across portions of the Piedmont
this morning, with visibilities under one half mile in some
locations. These areas of fog will likely linger through mid-
morning.
Use caution if traveling this morning. Use low beam headlights and
leave plenty of room between vehicles.</description>
